mmunity. While not being a group specific to the Canadian Rockies, there is a strong presence from the region.",[146,200,201,206,207,212],{},[149,202,205],{"href":203,"rel":204},"https:\u002F\u002Fgeartrade.ca\u002F",[153],"Geartrade"," is a ",[149,208,211],{"href":209,"rel":210},"https:\u002F\u002Fgeartrade.ca\u002Fpages\u002Fthe-geartrade-story",[153],"company founded in Okotoks, AB"," that provides great ultralight options.",[146,214,215,220,221,226],{},[149,216,219],{"href":217,"rel":218},"https:\u002F\u002Fdurstongear.com\u002F",[153],"Durston Gear"," is extremely popular among the Canadian Rockies ultralight community. The gear is ",[149,222,225],{"href":223,"rel":224},"https:\u002F\u002Fdurstongear.com\u002Fpages\u002Fabout",[153],"designed in the heart of the Rockies",".",[184,228,230],{"id":229},"electronics","Electronics",[143,232,233],{},[146,234,235,240,241,244],{},[149,236,239],{"href":237,"rel":238},"https:\u002F\u002Frockytalkie.ca\u002F",[153],"Rocky Talkie"," builds the backcountry radio that most of the community seems to swear by. ",[149,242,36],{"href":172,"rel":243},[153]," members get a 20% discount on Rocky Talkies.",{"title":246,"searchDepth":247,"depth":248,"links":249},"",1,2,[250],{"id":140,"depth":248,"text":141,"children":251},[252,254],{"id":186,"depth":253,"text":187},3,{"id":229,"depth":253,"text":230},"Because having the right gear makes the hike way more fun (and less cold\u002Fsoggy).","md",null,{},{"icon":104},{"title":10,"description":255},"_8vqlNZ62gQ5ePfVbaYgLzn_Wdbhhw9KDjtP0DuVgPg",[263,265],{"title":94,"path":95,"stem":96,"description":264,"icon":97,"children":-1},"Your go-to spots for updates on trail conditions and closures.",{"title":10,"path":107,"stem":108,"description":266,"icon":111,"children":-1},"Welcome to Alberta Hiking Resources.",1773623246172]